{"tid":1427494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【召喚分析撚】黑警成魔之路","createTime":"2019-08-07T06:24:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T09:24:15.000Z","uid":266362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6f16ab67aee7eaa12b990e75c6ba19f7c1bf2f2a","tid":1427494,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O75cOo8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO75cOo8.png&h=bafbff0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1MXCe4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1MXCe4i.png&h=1a315eb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇完 winter on fire 烏克蘭自由之戰，發現暴政下，天下黑警一樣黑，果度d黑軍黑警同香港黑警如出一轍，簡直係一撚樣，又係佔高位射民眾，又係玩催淚，又係失撚晒控狂扑民眾頭部，仲仆街到換走橡膠子彈射實彈，同埋炸救護站，射紅十字醫護人員，最後成場運動死撚咗好多人！<br />\n<br />\n運動中，當地民眾會同黑警講：<br />\n&gt;大家都係烏克蘭人<br />\n&gt;做咩殺人民<br />\n&gt;快d回到妻小身邊，快d回家喇<br />\n&gt;這個民族是不會被擊垮的<br />\n&gt;記唔記得你小時候的老師是怎樣教你<br />\n&gt;都唔明係怎樣的母親教出射殺救人的平民<br />\n等等等等<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNQ0XhM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNQ0XhM.png&h=71d093b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以忽發奇想，諗翻香港黑警（主要係諗員佐級果d散仔)，佢地係點解仲咁堅持自己並非有牌黑社會，堅稱係除暴安良。難道佢都真係做得好開心好過癮？難道佢地真係唔知自己失控？難道佢地真係唔知自己係黨國機器用完即棄？佢地心入面真係無自由、無公義、無普世價值？佢地真係唔知元朗白衣人係真暴徒無差別打市民？佢地又無建制議員、高官、中聯辦、政協委員咁cap水，點解仲咁傻做黑社會？真係純粹係IQ低？純粹係無自我反省？<br />\n<br />\n好想拎著塊鏡照住堆防暴黑警白衫，俾佢地望下鏡入面既陌生又冷血凶狠既自己！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好想分析完，從中搵到佢地既心理弱點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n公義必勝<br />\n真理必勝<br />\n自由必勝<br />\n暴政必亡"},{"pid":"b06964a2127e9e28fd3abecbea674433a3b2c3a3","tid":1427494,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:32:11.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"7841adc559b639db3ec6dfb82772ac061b92b847","tid":1427494,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:32:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"36aab90a3ebba4a7b1e59c4cc0fcd6db447aa21f","tid":1427494,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:32:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5724cb90df790311773e115b4658aae63cf6679e","tid":1427494,"uid":282634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"歡迎睇下「路西法效應」既相關資料"},{"pid":"5c7f96aeda2b61bd61195570d0a479be2e35b450","tid":1427494,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:35:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2X5W8mM_Wek&amp;t=1189s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2X5W8mM_Wek%26t%3D1189s&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75ZyK1%2BumEGLY4xtueqN3WuFY%3D&h=a2f19f0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2X5W8mM_Wek&amp;t=1189s</a>"},{"pid":"76e8dcf2b86da1a763f06e0cbddd4c9a28ee8be7","tid":1427494,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:42:27.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭人喊住講:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我不能接受，在世上發生如此多戰爭後，我們仍舊以互相殘殺來解決問題。</span></span>"},{"pid":"c6498ca31cdaa30c73d6b2e0049806026a55ecc4","tid":1427494,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:43:13.000Z","msg":"謝分享。一陣睇路西法。"},{"pid":"13d54a3d26f08399925a96870acb7349e9cd2f99","tid":1427494,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T09:24:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}